author: Associated Press
title: Florida man's gun discharges at a Dunkin' Dounts | Daily Mail Online
text: Florida man's gun drops from his clothing, discharges and a bullet hits a fellow customer at a Dunkin' Donuts on Saturday morning Randy Barroso, 38, and a 55-year-old woman were among those at a Florida Dunkin' Dounts Saturday morning Barroso's gun dropped from his clothing, discharged and a bullet hit the woman The woman was taken to a hospital for treatment of non-life-threatening injuries Barroso left the scene but later turned himself in to the police Said the shooting was unintentional and was arrested for culpable negligence Published: 22:04 GMT, 12 February 2017 | Updated: 03:53 GMT, 13 February 2017 117 shares
